.page-content
  %section.banner.-family
    .grid-container
      .grid-40
        %div
          %h1.heading.-large
            Finding the best health coverage for your personal needs and budget.
          %p
            Here at Benefit Choices, we offer our guidance in matching your individual or company requirements with the insurance plans that will work best for you. Our experienced insurance professionals are available to help you find solutions that meet your unique needs. We are dedicated to finding the plan that best serves you.
      .grid-60
        %br
  %section
    .grid-container
      .grid-100
        %h1.centered.heading.-large
          Questions about which health coverage options are right for you?
        %p.centered
          Our experienced agents are available to help.
        .centered
          = link_to 'Contact Us', new_email_path, :class => 'button -bright -large'
  %section.blue-herring
    .grid-container.padding-b3
      .grid-33.padding-lr3
        = image_tag image_url( 'medicare-logo.png' ), :alt => 'Medicare logo', :class => 'full-width'
      .grid-33.padding-lr3
        = image_tag image_url( 'medi-share-logo.png' ), :alt => 'Medicare logo', :class => 'full-width'
      .grid-33.padding-lr3
        = image_tag image_url( 'health.svg' ), :alt => 'Healthcare logo', :class => 'full-width'
    .grid-container
      .centered.grid-33
        %h2.heading.-medium
          Medicare
        %p
          With the large number of options that it offers to seniors, Medicare insurance can be difficult to navigate. Our Medicare-certified agents are happy to assist you in finding the right Medicare plan.
      .centered.grid-33
        %h2.centered.heading.-medium
          Medi-Share
        %p
          Chritian Health Care is a health expense option based on the principle of sharing medical needs as a community.
      .centered.grid-33
        %h2.centered.heading.-medium
          Everything Else
        %p
          We are also able to provide Accident, Dental, Disability, Life (whole, term, and universal), and Vision coverage options.
  %section
    .grid-container
      .grid-100
        %h1.heading.-large
          Marketplace Certified
